| Frontend (React) | 3000 | Self-Service-Portal |
| Backend (Node/Express) | 4000 | REST API, Webhooks |
| PostgreSQL | 5432 | Persistenz |
| Redis | 6379 | Cache (Berechtigungen) |
| GitHub Actions | — | CI/CD, Provisioning |

